song_the_chain.track_name: Gone With The Wind Is My Love

segue_dave.line: The album "Richie Haven Sings Beatles and Dylan" by Richie Havens is a tribute to Bob Dylan, and the same album is also a tribute to The Beatles...
segue_dave.explanation: Bob Dylan is a tribute to the record Richie Haven Sings Beatles and Dylan and The Beatles is a tribute to the record Richie Haven Sings Beatles and Dylan
